data: As a third-year student studying for a Bachelor's degree in Computer Science at the IUT in Lannion, I am aiming for a career in software or web development. I therefore plan to continue my studies by enrolling in an engineering school or a master's program.
In order to validate my third year of a Bachelor's degree in Computer Science, I am looking for a 14-week internship starting on March 23, 2026.
